		effects: [
			{
				type: ExtraCost
				cost: [
					{
						type: Hinder
						select: choose(beacon)
						count: 2
					}
				]
			}

			{
				type: Response
				trigger: {
					type: AboutToTakeWound
					filter: unbound, Man
					memorize: woundedMan
				}
				cost: [
					{
						type: Spot
						filter: beacon
						count: {
							type: TwilightCostInMemory
							memory: woundedMan
						}
					}
					{
						type: Hinder
						select: choose(beacon)
					}
				]
				effect: {
					type: PreventWound
					select: memory(woundedMan)
				}
			}
		]
		gametext: Beacon. To play, hinder 2 beacons.<br>Response: If an unbound Man costing X is about to take a wound, spot X beacons to prevent that wound. Hinder a beacon.
		lore: "'On, Shadowfax! We must hasten. Time is short. See! The beacons of Gondor are alight, calling for aid. War is kindled.'"
